id":"f537dfff12","type":"subtitle","text":"34．大力开展整风运动认清两种立场、两种态度。","index":130,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ab2374011c"},{"id":"7b05aaab85","type":"paragraph","text":"整风运动开始，可是为什么有些党员那样消极、沉默。他们在说：“等把事实弄清楚再说吧”，大字报有些夸大，应该冷静分析考虑这些问题。”我们不禁要问：你们为什么在三反、五反、肃反运动中那样积极？要大胆怀疑发动群众，使劲斗用力打，面对已经知道斗错了的却没有公开的更正。现在整风运动刚开始，有人就喊：“要把事实弄清楚，不要盲目行动，反对不加分析的否定党团一切的作法，要和风细雨，反对一棒子打死人等等”。我们不禁要问：“你们是大力开展整风运动，还是限制整风运动发展，是整风运动还是表功运动，你们是真正维护党的利益，还是维护几个党员的错误？现在我们高呼：反对右倾保守思想，大力开展整风运动，我们要撕掉他们身上各种护身符，不允许作任何的逃避掩饰，要老爷们正视自己的错误，要倾听群众的呼声。我们反对包办式的代表会议制度，要彻底消灭包办制度，发动群众大力开展整风运动。(除害社六一  田少文)","index":131,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ab2374011c"},{"id":"8b9d653605","type":"subtitle","text":"35．马雅可夫斯基与官僚主义者的对话。","index":132,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ab2374011c"},{"id":"201be6ed9a","type":"paragraph","text":"官：马雅可夫斯基同志不客气的说，你的诗很不好，如：我真象狼一样的吃掉官僚主义，请问这是解决内部矛盾的态度吗？","index":133,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ab2374011c"},{"id":"15fe1d9a9e","type":"paragraph","text":"马：你的意思怎样呢？","index":134,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ab2374011c"},{"id":"e8d00a00f5","type":"paragraph","text":"官：我的意思是请你修改一下，温和些。例如：把狼改为“绵羊”“家兔”或“猫”……","index":135,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ab2374011c"},{"id":"7cdd620d9f","type":"paragraph","text":"马雅可夫斯基同志笑着说：首长同志，按你的意思修改，我的诗应该是这样的：","index":136,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ab2374011c"},{"id":"f9cb57bac9","type":"paragraph","text":"我真象绵羊一样地歌唱官僚主义。","index":137,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ab2374011c"},{"id":"cfabae1376","type":"paragraph","text":"我真象家兔一样地吻官僚主义。","index":138,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ab2374011c"},{"id":"4eba7aa55b","type":"paragraph","text":"我真象猫一样地舐官僚主义。","index":139,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ab2374011c"},{"id":"236da8d09e","type":"paragraph","text":"首长微笑着拍着掌说：","index":140,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ab2374011c"},{"id":"3e56976938","type":"paragraph","text":"太好了！马雅可夫斯基同志就这样，就这样…… (文三讽刺窗)","index":141,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ab2374011c"},{"id":"c439569ccd","type":"subtitle","text":"36．他是党员嘛！","index":142,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ab2374011c"},{"id":"0b9ee79e4c","type":"paragraph","text":"学生：因病申请补助费。","index":143,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ab2374011c"},{"id":"a0770268c0","type":"paragraph","text":"朱院长：你先和学生科汪祥谈一谈。","index":144,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ab2374011c"},{"id":"b09d570a70","type":"paragraph","text":"学生：已和他谈过，他对工作有偏见。","index":145,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ab2374011c"},{"id":"fd854bff1a","type":"paragraph","text":"朱院长：他是党员！","index":146,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ab2374011c"},{"id":"e2e34da3b8","type":"paragraph","text":"学生：啊！(史三库里亚)","index":147,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ab2374011c"},{"id":"3f9e161eb3","type":"subtitle","text":"37．吸收党员标准。","index":148,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ab2374011c"},{"id":"52431cdced","type":"paragraph","text":"支书：我们吸收×××为党员。","index":149,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ab2374011c"},{"id":"2a8387033a","type":"paragraph","text":"党委会：这个同志一贯表现如何？","index":150,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ab2374011c"},{"id":"6f1127a9f8","type":"paragraph","text":"支书：一贯表现老老实实、服服从从，能完成领导意图，从来不提反对意见。","index":151,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ab2374011c"},{"id":"641cf2b281","type":"paragraph","text":"党委会：批准！批准！(文三讽刺窗)","index":152,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ab2374011c"},{"id":"dd8d604c08","type":"subtitle","text":"38．衙门似的脸。","index":153,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ab2374011c"},{"id":"92154477aa","type":"paragraph","text":"办公室的干部——凉冰冰，","index":154,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ab2374011c"},{"id":"7d504a3391","type":"paragraph","text":"治保会的干部——阴森森，","index":155,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ab2374011c"},{"id":"5b9c4c787f","type":"paragraph","text":"他们的脸——千年不见一笑，","index":156,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ab2374011c"},{"id":"cd5091582a",